Package: glycoreach
Title: Glycan Reachability Analysis from Transcriptomics
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yusuke", "Matsui", email = "mail.to.matsui@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Computes glycan biosynthetic reachability scores from gene expression
    data using AND/OR logic and min-aggregation (bottleneck principle). Supports
    sialyl Lewis X, ganglioside, heparan sulfate, N-glycan, and O-GalNAc pathways.
    Applicable to bulk RNA-seq, pseudobulk single-cell, or any gene expression matrix.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    data.table,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/matsui-lab/glycoreach
BugReports: https://github.com/matsui-lab/glycoreach/issues
